tags.fixme: Improve park boundary so that this falls on it.
tags.note: Line of posts, rather than proper bollards.  This forms an entrance to the park.  However, there is no formal footpath.
This is not a roundabout, because left turning traffic has priority. See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traffic_circle and https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Traffic_circle#Possible_misinterpretations
Although this is technically two way, the there is no way in eastbound, other than a U turn and the eastbound side is in a poor state of repair.

tags.cycleway:note: Although to the left of the traffic, the lane is often to the right of parking spaces.
